676
01:10:35,931 --> 01:10:39,230
I'm okay. I only want you to be happy.

677
01:10:46,408 --> 01:10:48,035
No matter what happens...

678
01:10:50,913 --> 01:10:53,006
You must let me know.

679
01:10:56,185 --> 01:10:57,413
If there's a way...

680
01:10:59,688 --> 01:11:01,246
I'll send for you.

681
01:11:10,232 --> 01:11:12,132
Don't say anymore.

682
01:11:14,236 --> 01:11:16,568
I thought we have an understanding:

683
01:11:24,313 --> 01:11:28,306
Nothing will change ifwe don't talk about it.

684
01:11:30,352 --> 01:11:35,722
Nothing will ever change
ifwe never say a word about it.

685
01:12:12,628 --> 01:12:16,325
The days slipped away quietly in expectation.

686
01:12:17,132 --> 01:12:21,967
Father always wore a worried look on his face.

687
01:12:23,205 --> 01:12:26,834
Hou Jia and I wrote furiously to each other.

688
01:12:26,875 --> 01:12:27,933
He told me that

689
01:12:28,277 --> 01:12:32,907
He'd collected over a dozen editions
ofRomeo and Juliet in different languages.

690
01:12:33,515 --> 01:12:37,246
The days went by, and that was our link.

691
01:12:38,253 --> 01:12:41,780
Romeo and Juliet die for their love.

692
01:12:42,224 --> 01:12:46,718
We die for our love with each other's solitude.

693
01:12:52,101 --> 01:12:53,090
Thank you.

694
01:12:53,135 --> 01:12:55,399
Have some watermelon. Thank you.

695
01:12:55,637 --> 01:12:58,162
Cool you off in this hot weather.
That's so true.

696
