Mom.

697
01:13:01,677 --> 01:13:03,338
Ranran, look who's here.

698
01:13:03,545 --> 01:13:04,534
Ranran.

699
01:13:04,580 --> 01:13:05,569
Mrs. Feng, how are you?

700
01:13:05,614 --> 01:13:06,581
How are you?

701
01:13:06,615 --> 01:13:11,052
It's been ages. You're all grown up,
and so beautiful.

702
01:13:12,521 --> 01:13:14,489
Hey, leave my bag alone.

703
01:13:15,958 --> 01:13:20,395
Ranran, Mrs. Feng is here about your business.
Sit down for a while.

704
01:13:21,697 --> 01:13:23,722
Mrs. Feng, please make yourself at home.
I have to work.

705
01:13:23,766 --> 01:13:24,460
Sure.

706
01:13:24,500 --> 01:13:25,489
Ranran.

707
01:13:25,868 --> 01:13:26,960
I really have to work.

708
01:13:27,903 --> 01:13:30,030
Please sit down.

709
01:13:30,372 --> 01:13:31,361
Have some watermelon.

710
01:13:31,407 --> 01:13:32,533
To cool off.

711
01:13:32,808 --> 01:13:33,797
Thanks

712
01:13:34,810 --> 01:13:36,835
This watermelon is great. Right.

713
01:13:38,714 --> 01:13:39,703
Have some water.

714
01:13:39,748 --> 01:13:41,545
Thank you.

715
01:13:41,750 --> 01:13:45,447
I've brought with me a photograph. Here.

716
01:14:07,843 --> 01:14:10,243
Seoul, scattered showers, 15 to 25 degrees.

717
01:14:13,682 --> 01:14:16,810
Beijing, scattered showers to overcast,
12 to 17 degrees.

718
01:14:29,565 --> 01:14:32,329
Ranran, Mrs. Feng rode on the bus
for two hours to visit us...

719
01:14:32,634 --> 01:14:35,364
To talk about your business...

720
01:14:35,771 --> 01:14:37,534
And you wouldn't even sit down with her.

721
01:14:38,941 --> 01:14:40,374
I have nothing to say to her.

722
01:14:41,410 --> 01:14:44,846
Mom, it's only clothes for the child,
don't fret over them.

723
