We're not obliged to serve you.

728
01:15:04,800 --> 01:15:07,030
You just can't go out and hang yourself on a tree.

729
01:15:10,372 --> 01:15:14,172
To hang myself or not, that's my own business.

730
01:15:15,043 --> 01:15:16,567
What do you mean that's your own business?

731
01:15:17,412 --> 01:15:19,437
Look what you did to our parents!

732
01:15:20,582 --> 01:15:22,641
Look what you did to this family!

733
01:15:23,051 --> 01:15:26,282
When the nanny arrives,
you get ready to move into the sitting room.

734
01:15:27,055 --> 01:15:28,044
Shut up.

735
01:15:30,125 --> 01:15:35,563
This is my home, and Ranran will always
have a room in this home.

736
01:15:37,032 --> 01:15:41,526
If need be, I move into the sitting room.

737
01:15:46,675 --> 01:15:50,270
Mom, eat. I'll make some more.

738
01:15:55,551 --> 01:15:59,419
I shouldn't have said that.

739
01:16:00,689 --> 01:16:01,713
It's just that...

740
01:16:02,691 --> 01:16:04,488
I worry about you.

741
01:16:06,862 --> 01:16:07,886
Brother...

742
01:16:09,731 --> 01:16:17,263
How come you can be with the person you love and l
cannot?

743
01:16:50,806 --> 01:16:51,795
Ranran...

744
01:16:53,675 --> 01:16:55,074
I'm not asking you to do anything for anyone...

745
01:16:56,712 --> 01:16:58,942
Just for yourself.

746
01:17:01,917 --> 01:17:03,612
Oh...

747
01:17:08,090 --> 01:17:10,388
Not even thirty...

748
01:17:11,627 --> 01:17:13,686
And you already have white hair.

749
01:17:22,938 --> 01:17:27,341
Qu Ran, come look at Hou Jia's picture.

750
01:17:29,745 --> 01:17:30,905
I just got it in the mail.

751
01:17:43,525 --> 01:17:44,992
That's nice.

752
01:18:09,284 --> 01:18:11,377
What about my line to Boston?

753
01:18:11,620 --> 01:18:13,645
We're very busy today, please wait another minute.

754
01:18:14,923 --> 01:18:17,118
Line to Paris, booth number 3.

755
01:18:59,601 --> 01:19:03,799
The story that begins with
a bang ends with a whimper.

756
01:19:05,006 --> 01:19:11,707
For the first time in my life,
I felt lonely, like I've been dumped.

757
01:19:12,981 --> 01:19:18,476
I decided to stop contacting Hou Jia,
afraid that he'd confirm that ending...

758
01:19:19,454 --> 01:19:23,220
That he'd tell me things that
I didn't want to know.

759
01:19:44,379 --> 01:19:47,644
Baobao, say Happy new year to grandparent

760
01:19:47,883 --> 01:19:50,647
As well as auntie. Don't forget!

761
01:19:56,091 --> 01:19:57,615
Baobao, here.

762
01:19:58,627 --> 01:20:03,462
She always gives you the biggest red packet.

763
01:20:04,432 --> 01:20:07,924
Stop giving him so much money. He's just a kid.

764
01:20:08,303 --> 01:20:10,362
I make my money for him anyway.

765
01:20:11,373 --> 01:20:14,365
Baobao, you be nice to Auntie Ranran
when you grow up.

766
01:20:17,078 --> 01:20:20,741
When Baobao grows up,
he'll buy a country house for his grandparents.

767
01:20:21,883 --> 01:20:23,248
I'll buy one for Auntie Ranran.

768
01:20:23,285 --> 01:20:24,274
Buy what?

769
01:20:24,386 --> 01:20:25,375
A country house.

770
01:21:38,393 --> 01:21:39,382
Let's get one.

771
01:21:39,494 --> 01:21:40,654
Why?

772
01:21:41,296 --> 01:21:42,763
For Baobao.

773
01:21:43,465 --> 01:21:45,160
I don't think he doesn't want it.

774
01:21:45,500 --> 01:21:46,489
Then I want if for myself.

775
01:21:50,372 --> 01:21:51,464
It's so cute.

776
01:21:53,275 --> 01:21:54,640
I want two.

777
01:22:04,452 --> 01:22:06,147
My son said when he had money

778
01:22:06,721 --> 01:22:10,384
He'd right away find me an apartment
with an elevator.

779
01:22:10,792 --> 01:22:13,522
I said let's wait until
you came back but he insisted.

780
01:22:13,828 --> 01:22:15,193
Where is she moving to?

781
01:22:15,664 --> 01:22:16,995
I don't know.

782
01:22:19,668 --> 01:22:20,657
Goodbye.

783
01:22:21,202 --> 01:22:22,294
Come visit me when you have time.

784
01:22:22,337 --> 01:22:23,770
Yes, of course.

785
01:22:24,005 --> 01:22:25,302
You all come.

