01:23:57,799 --> 01:24:01,360
Let me get you a pair if you like them.

798
01:25:39,434 --> 01:25:41,925
Bangkok, thunderstorm, 25 to 33 degrees.

799
01:25:46,307 --> 01:25:48,798
San Francisco, sunny, 13 to 22 degrees.

800
01:25:53,281 --> 01:25:55,146
London, overcast, 9 to 19 degrees.

801
01:26:00,054 --> 01:26:02,852
Karachi, sunny, 27 to 35 degrees.

802
01:26:07,195 --> 01:26:09,789
Moscow, showers, 4 to 16 degrees.

803
01:26:57,111 --> 01:26:58,169
it's been two weeks since I returned to China

804
01:26:59,614 --> 01:27:00,876
and I haven't visited Qu Ran

805
01:27:02,817 --> 01:27:05,251
I was afraid that she's moved on

806
01:27:06,621 --> 01:27:11,923
But somehow I felt I should go to
that show with Qu Ran

807
01:27:46,227 --> 01:27:48,627
Why am I coming to see this show?.

808
01:27:50,265 --> 01:27:54,258
Why can't I cut myself offfrom this story?

809
01:27:55,870 --> 01:27:57,804
Perhaps I've given up having expectations.

810
01:27:59,073 --> 01:28:02,634
It's just that waiting has become my life.

811
01:28:26,167 --> 01:28:29,694
Stop looking for it. It disappeared ages ago.

812
01:28:32,540 --> 01:28:36,874
There's a stamp of Qu Ran's stamp on that book.
You must have thrown it out.

813
01:28:39,714 --> 01:28:41,375
The maid does the cleaning up.

814
01:28:42,150 --> 01:28:44,380
I cannot remember everything.

815
01:28:45,453 --> 01:28:48,945
You may forget other things,
but certainly not that book.

816
01:28:50,124 --> 01:28:51,921
You took it out form my chest.

817
01:28:53,127 --> 01:28:59,066
It's for you own good. Do you hate me for it?

818
01:29:01,235 --> 01:29:02,668
How can I feel warmth?

819
01:29:03,004 --> 01:29:05,495
All I wanted was to come back early
and take care of you...

820
01:29:06,341 --> 01:29:08,002
To make you happy and healthy.

821
01:29:08,943 --> 01:29:11,002
Why do I want to live long?

822
01:29:11,612 --> 01:29:14,809
To look at my son stay single
for the rest ofhis life?

823
01:29:24,192 --> 01:29:25,318
I heard Hou Jia came back.

824
01:29:26,661 --> 01:29:28,151
He's been gone six or seven years, rights?

825
01:29:30,898 --> 01:29:31,887
Seven years.

826
01:29:33,601 --> 01:29:36,365
What're you two going to do?

827
01:29:38,740 --> 01:29:41,368
That's ancient history.
Let's don't bring it up again.

828
01:29:42,944 --> 01:29:45,572
Do you have any plans for yourself?.

829
01:29:47,448 --> 01:29:55,378
Dad, sometimes I really want to get married.

830
01:29:59,026 --> 01:30:03,463
But you know, these things...

831
01:30:07,402 --> 01:30:11,702
I'll just stay with you and mom, make myselfthis
piece of junk useful.

832
01:30:19,480 --> 01:30:21,744
I'm going to the hospital tomorrow for my report.

833
01:30:22,850 --> 01:30:24,010
I'll go with you.

834
01:30:24,652 --> 01:30:29,521
No, your mom can go with me.

835
01:30:50,578 --> 01:30:51,567
I went back to the building
of my youth and childhood

836
01:30:51,913 --> 01:30:53,312
Nothing has changed.

837
01:30:54,816 --> 01:30:56,044
Qu Ran wasn't home.

838
01:30:57,218 --> 01:30:58,617
I only saw her mother and left my card.

839
01:30:59,187 --> 01:31:01,451
He left a business card,
but I didn't have time for him.

840
01:31:37,191 --> 01:31:38,180
Mom.

841
01:31:43,164 --> 01:31:44,392
Ranran.

842
01:31:45,266 --> 01:31:48,235
Your father's report came out.

843
01:31:50,705 --> 01:31:51,694
It's not good.

844
01:32:10,324 --> 01:32:16,194
It's my fault. I made him suffer.

845
01:32:16,230 --> 01:32:27,368
Stop this nonsense.
Your father said he didn't want an operation.

846
01:32:37,118 --> 01:32:41,714
My father's illness made me realize
how deeply I'd hurt him.

847
01:32:42,957 --> 01:32:48,224
Hou Qia came to see me but
I didn't have any time for him

848
01:33:10,384 --> 01:33:11,510
Dad.

849
01:33:11,986 --> 01:33:13,317
Oh.

850
01:33:14,055 --> 01:33:15,488
Time for your medicine.

851
01:33:32,473 --> 01:33:33,599
Ranran.

852
01:33:44,485 --> 01:33:46,612
Give Hou Jia a call.

853
01:33:50,625 --> 01:33:51,614
He's always busy.

854
01:33:53,260 --> 01:33:55,660
Just to get together, for old time's sake.

855
01:35:07,034 --> 01:35:08,023
Hello.

856
01:35:09,070 --> 01:35:14,906
This is Qu Zhiheng. My cancer's terminal,
and I don't know...

857
01:35:15,509 --> 01:35:20,412
Ifl could still have the opportunity
to apologize to you in person.

858
01:35:23,684 --> 01:35:29,680
If possible, please have Hou Jia
come over to my house...

859
01:35:31,192 --> 01:35:35,856
There's something that I'd like to say to him.

860
01:35:59,386 --> 01:36:06,315
Do you still remember that day when
you confronted me in the courtyard?

861
01:36:11,298 --> 01:36:16,201
I shouldn't have behaved like that,
I do apologize.

862
01:36:17,138 --> 01:36:22,599
It was so long ago.
Please don't make it difficult for yourself.

863
01:36:23,944 --> 01:36:28,540
Hou Jia, I've done Ranran harm.

864
01:36:29,984 --> 01:36:32,179
My biggest sorrow...

865
01:36:33,521 --> 01:36:36,251
Is to see my daughter...

866
01:36:37,525 --> 01:36:39,493
Year after year,

867
01:36:40,294 --> 01:36:42,319
Lose her youth...

868
01:36:44,498 --> 01:36:47,626
Until she's turned into an old maid.

869
01:36:48,536 --> 01:36:50,970
I, as her father...

870
01:36:52,273 --> 01:36:55,071
Had ruined her chance for a happy life.

871
01:36:57,344 --> 01:36:58,777
Uncle Qu.

872
01:37:00,481 --> 01:37:05,111
If you could accept my apology...

873
01:37:06,220 --> 01:37:11,351
I wish you and Ranran would get married.

874
01:37:14,995 --> 01:37:20,991
This is a letter that I wrote to the organization.
It stated that...

875
01:37:21,969 --> 01:37:25,769
Out of concern for the girl...

876
01:37:25,806 --> 01:37:27,831
I had indeed told her that...

877
01:37:28,175 --> 01:37:33,272
If she was forced into it,
then she was only the victim.

878
01:37:33,647 --> 01:37:37,549
So I was responsible for your father's death.

879
01:37:40,621 --> 01:37:42,851
If your mother finds it necessary...

880
01:37:43,724 --> 01:37:51,688
She can take this letter to the organization and
request them to re-open the file.

881
01:39:18,118 --> 01:39:21,815
Why don't you invite Qu Ran
to visit your new home?

882
01:39:30,364 --> 01:39:35,768
What's wrong with you? The phone's ringing.

883
01:40:17,211 --> 01:40:18,200
Qu Ran.

884
01:40:18,612 --> 01:40:19,601
It's me.

885
01:40:21,148 --> 01:40:22,445
How's your mom?

886
01:40:23,984 --> 01:40:25,611
Is she okay?

887
01:40:27,621 --> 01:40:31,057
Give her my regards. You take care of yourself.

888
01:40:33,293 --> 01:40:35,887
Try to spend more time with her.

889
01:40:36,697 --> 01:40:37,857
Yes.

890
01:40:38,432 --> 01:40:40,263
There's something that
I've always wanted to ask you.

891
01:40:40,300 --> 01:40:43,201
What is it? Please

892
01:40:45,239 --> 01:40:47,173
All those years we were separated.

893
01:40:48,208 --> 01:40:51,302
Now we can see each other again,
but we're not. Why?

894
01:40:52,646 --> 01:40:57,208
My father has died;
and you know how much I'd hurt him

895
01:40:58,152 --> 01:40:59,414
But Qu Ran... he...

896
01:40:59,453 --> 01:41:04,755
Hou Qia, we can never meet
the departed again, ever.

897
01:42:33,046 --> 01:42:35,207
I started living by myself.

898
01:42:36,350 --> 01:42:38,477
I didn't see or call Qu Ran.

899
01:42:39,720 --> 01:42:40,709
At that time I thought:

900
01:42:41,388 --> 01:42:45,654
Shakespeare's love story has brought us together
so many times before.

901
01:42:47,261 --> 01:42:48,626
Now there's a new scenario,
can we still get together?

902
01:42:50,430 --> 01:42:51,419
Somewhere, somehow....

903
01:42:51,965 --> 01:42:55,958
Will she and I brush past calmly?

904
01:43:04,678 --> 01:43:06,475
Excuse me. Please wait.

905
01:43:08,582 --> 01:43:09,606
Right, that's it.

906
01:43:12,586 --> 01:43:13,883
C'mon, don't lag behind.

907
01:43:22,696 --> 01:43:23,685
It's pretty good.

908
01:43:33,273 --> 01:43:34,501
You should also try it on when you time comes.

909
01:44:16,717 --> 01:44:17,706
What are you doing here?

910
01:44:17,751 --> 01:44:18,809
Let me go say hello to a friend.

911
01:44:19,286 --> 01:44:20,275
Qu Ran.

912
01:44:22,322 --> 01:44:23,311
You're...

913
01:44:24,124 --> 01:44:26,354
It's my colleague.

914
01:44:27,227 --> 01:44:28,216
Is it?

915
01:44:29,896 --> 01:44:35,857
She wants to rent a wedding gown,
especially that one in the window.

916
01:44:42,175 --> 01:44:43,870
I thought...

917
01:44:47,247 --> 01:44:50,842
She looks older than you.

918
01:44:52,886 --> 01:44:55,116
It's her third marriage.

919
01:45:11,772 --> 01:45:17,233
Sir, buy a flower for the lady. Thank you.

920
01:45:18,779 --> 01:45:20,246
Buy a flower please.

921
01:45:21,381 --> 01:45:23,076
Happy Valentine.

922
01:45:23,650 --> 01:45:28,644
Young people today celebrate Valentine,
I guess that's fashionable.

923
01:45:30,057 --> 01:45:33,993
People are living better and
there're more festivities.

924
01:45:35,495 --> 01:45:36,621
Right.

925
01:45:37,431 --> 01:45:39,399
We've been left behind.

926
01:45:41,401 --> 01:45:44,336
It's only lovers who are not married
that celebrate Valentine.

927
01:45:48,408 --> 01:45:50,239
In any case, for the occasion...

928
01:45:51,144 --> 01:45:52,702
I also brought you a small present.

929
01:45:53,280 --> 01:45:55,441
What are you doing? Look at our age.

930
01:46:09,196 --> 01:46:11,130
I've always worried that you'd give up.

931
01:46:12,699 --> 01:46:14,667
All these years it's been torturing me.

932
01:46:17,070 --> 01:46:20,631
Nothing will change ifwe don't talk about it...

933
01:46:21,408 --> 01:46:26,436
Nothing will ever change if
we don't ever say a word about it.

934
01:46:33,286 --> 01:46:34,378
Qu Ran.

935
01:46:37,524 --> 01:46:39,185
Let's get married.

936
01:46:41,194 --> 01:46:42,661
I want to make you happy.

937
01:46:55,609 --> 01:46:57,577
To live with you in the same building...

938
01:46:59,513 --> 01:47:01,845
That was once my happiness.

939
01:47:05,118 --> 01:47:07,018
To live with you in the same city...

940
01:47:08,555 --> 01:47:10,147
That's also once my happiness.

941
01:47:18,598 --> 01:47:21,590
To be alive with you at the same time
in this world...

942
01:47:22,202 --> 01:47:24,363
That will be my happiness.

943
01:47:27,774 --> 01:47:29,264
Happiness...

944
01:47:31,878 --> 01:47:34,506
Is a feeling from deep inside your heart.

945
01:48:22,929 --> 01:48:24,021
Hi, this way please

946
01:48:28,401 --> 01:48:29,390
Stand over there a bit.

947
01:48:29,436 --> 01:48:30,801
Get close to each other.

948
01:48:33,507 --> 01:48:34,496
Right.

949
01:48:38,411 --> 01:48:39,400
Look this way.

950
01:48:40,514 --> 01:48:41,845
We're doing the first set.

951
01:48:44,518 --> 01:48:45,780
Don't move.

952
01:48:46,786 --> 01:48:48,117
Look this way.

953
01:48:52,592 --> 01:48:53,581
The bride...

954
01:48:53,660 --> 01:48:54,718
The bride please smile.

955
01:49:01,601 --> 01:49:03,262
The bride please smiles again.

956
01:49:05,572 --> 01:49:06,869
Look this way.

957
01:49:09,042 --> 01:49:10,805
Ready...

958
01:49:11,912 --> 01:49:13,402
Ready...
